Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.cards.leader

Class StorageAbility

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.cards.leader.StorageAbility
All Implemented Interfaces:
Card, LeaderCard
public class StorageAbility
extends java.lang.Object
implements LeaderCard
This LeaderCard gives you an extra special 2-slot depot. This special depot can only store the indicated Resources. You can also store the same type of Resource in a basic Warehouse depot.

In order to activate the card, players must have all the production cards specified in cost, even if they're hidden. Use the isActive() method to discover its status.
